    the TSA loss L(θ) converges to a local minimum at rate O(1/√k)
    where k is the iteration number.
    
    ASSUMPTIONS:
    1. Loss is L-smooth
    2. Surrogate gradient is unbiased estimator
    3. Learning rate η_k = η_0/√k
    
    PROOF:
    """
    
